<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:orientation="vertical"
    android:background="@color/background"
    tools:context=".MealDetails">

    <FrameLayout
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
        android:paddingVertical="8dp"
        android:background="@drawable/background_header">

        <com.google.android.flexbox.FlexboxLayout
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            app:justifyContent="space_between"
            app:alignItems="center">

            <com.google.android.flexbox.FlexboxLayout
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                app:alignItems="center">

                <ImageView
                    android:layout_width="43dp"
                    android:layout_height="40dp"
                    android:src="@drawable/logo"
                    android:layout_marginEnd="4dp"/>

                <TextView
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:text="GhostChef"
                    android:textSize="26sp"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:textStyle="bold"
                    android:includeFontPadding="false"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/poppinssemibold"/>

            </com.google.android.flexbox.FlexboxLayout>

            <ImageButton
                android:id="@+id/buttonOpenDialog"
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:background="@drawable/background_primary_button"
                android:padding="8dp"
                android:src="@drawable/icon_sparkles"/>

        </com.google.android.flexbox.FlexboxLayout>

    </FrameLayout>

    <FrameLayout
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent" >

        <ScrollView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="match_parent" >

            <LinearLayout
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:orientation="vertical">

                <ImageView
                    android:id="@+id/ImageViewMealImage"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="260dp"
                    android:src="@drawable/meal_image_0"
                    android:scaleType="centerCrop"
                    android:layout_marginBottom="16dp"/>

                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp">

                    <TextView
                        android:id="@+id/TextViewMealTitle"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginBottom="8dp"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/poppinssemibold"
                        android:includeFontPadding="false"
                        android:text="Protein Packed Burrito"
                        android:textColor="@color/black"
                        android:textSize="24sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold" />

                    <TextView
                        android:id="@+id/TextViewMealDescription"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginBottom="16dp"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/poppinsregular"
                        android:includeFontPadding="false"
                        android:text="The Protein Packed Burrito is a delicious and nutritious meal that is filled with high-protein ingredients to fuel your body."
                        android:textColor="@color/neutral"
                        android:textSize="16sp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginBottom="8dp"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/poppinssemibold"
                        android:includeFontPadding="false"
                        android:text="Ingredients"
                        android:textColor="@color/black"
                        android:textSize="20sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold" />

                    <TextView
                        android:id="@+id/TextViewMealIngredients"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginBottom="16dp"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/poppinsregular"
                        android:includeFontPadding="false"
                        android:text="Scrambled tofu\nFresh jalape単o peppers\nFresh greens\nAvocado\nZingy hot sauceBlack beans (optional)\nSriracha (optional)"
                        android:textColor="@color/neutral"
                        android:textSize="16sp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginBottom="8dp"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/poppinssemibold"
                        android:includeFontPadding="false"
                        android:text="Instructions"
                        android:textColor="@color/black"
                        android:textSize="20sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold" />

                    <TextView
                        android:id="@+id/TextViewMealInstructions"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginBottom="84dp"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/poppinsregular"
                        android:includeFontPadding="false"
                        android:text="Prepare the scrambled tofu: In a non-stick pan, crumble the tofu and cook it over medium heat until it resembles scrambled eggs. Season with salt and pepper to taste.\n\nAdd the fresh jalape単o peppers: Finely chop the fresh jalape単o peppers and add them to the pan with the scrambled tofu. Cook for a few minutes until the peppers are softened.\n\nPrepare the fresh greens: Wash and chop the fresh greens of your choice, such as lettuce or spinach.\n\nSlice the avocado: Cut the avocado in half, remove the pit, and slice it into thin pieces.\n\nWarm the tortilla: Heat a tortilla in a dry pan or microwave until it is warm and pliable.\n\nAssemble the burrito: Lay the warm tortilla flat and spread a generous amount of the scrambled tofu and jalape単o mixture onto the center. Top it with fresh greens, sliced avocado, and a drizzle of zingy hot sauce. If desired, you can also add black beans or a drizzle of Sriracha for extra flavor and protein.Roll the burrito: Fold the sides of the tortilla over the filling, then roll it tightly from one end to the other, creating a burrito shape.\n\nServe and enjoy: Cut the burrito in half if desired and serve it immediately. Enjoy your Protein Packed Burrito as a satisfying and nutritious meal!"
                        android:textColor="@color/neutral"
                        android:textSize="16sp" />

                </LinearLayout>

            </LinearLayout>

        </ScrollView>

        <Button
            android:id="@+id/buttonGenerateMeal"
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_gravity="bottom|center"
            android:layout_marginBottom="16dp"
            android:text="Generate Meal"
            android:textAllCaps="false"
            android:includeFontPadding="false"
            android:drawableEnd="@drawable/icon_magic_wand"
            android:drawablePadding="8dp"
            android:background="@drawable/background_primary_button"
            android:theme="@style/buttonPrimary"/>
    </FrameLayout>

</LinearLayout>
